function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)

-- NPC calls to the player for help.
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(S_CONV_HELP, idNPC)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	-- Enable spawners
	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tMonsters) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then
			Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, false)
		end
	end
end

function Start(flTimeRemaining)

	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idNPC, 1)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idNPC, S_FX_BLOODIMPACT, false, Hydra.ACDID_INVALID, "HP_Chest")
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	Hydra.QActorKill(idNPC)
end
